Standard and Poor's Corp said it isreviewing for downgrade United Artists Communications Inc'ssingle-B rating on 490 mln dlrs of outstanding andshelf-registered subordinated debt.    Placed under review with positive implications were UnitedCable Television Corp's B-minus rating on 250 mln dlrs ofoutstanding subordinated debt and preliminary B-plus senior andB-minus subordinated ratings on 200 mln dlrs ofshelf-registered debt.    S and P said the reviews reflect its perception of theimplications of a proposed merger involving the two firms. Reuter&#3;